FireStrike began to walk down the hall and turned to talk to NS.  " 
Listen to me closely brother.  We were created to follow leaders, 
never to follow our sparks energy waves.  They are what we must 
follow and they will lead us to the destruction of all. Think about 
it , if you jsut follow someone elses spark, one spark how far can 
you get. But if everyoen follows there own and heads towards an 
ultimate goal, success is garunteed."
